      "4": "kai poreuetai epi asemwna kai diekbalei ews faraggos aiguptou kai estai autou h diexodos twn oriwn epi thn qalassan touto estin autwn oria apo libos",
      "5": "kai ta oria apo anatolwn pasa h qalassa h alukh ews tou iordanou kai ta oria autwn apo borra kai apo ths lofias ths qalasshs kai apo tou merous tou iordanou",
      "6": "epibainei ta oria epi baiqagla kai paraporeuetai apo borra epi baiqaraba kai prosanabainei ta oria epi liqon baiwn uiou roubhn",
